headline: AAR Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Sales Increase Year Over Year
summary: AIR's total sales in the third quarter of fiscal 2025 misses the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 3%. However, the top line increases 19.5% from the year-ago level.
